        <HeadLine>Michael Douglas, Catherine Zeta-Jones appear in court in stalking case</HeadLine>
        
        <DateLine>LOS ANGELES (AFP)</DateLine>
        <CopyrightLine>© 2004 AFP</CopyrightLine>
